37:47.178 --> 37:48.510
Speak!

37:48.512 --> 37:50.846
I will go no further.

37:50.848 --> 37:52.748
I am thy father's spirit,

37:52.750 --> 37:56.251
doomed for a certain term to walk the night,

37:56.253 --> 38:00.488
