confined to fast in fires...

38:00.490 --> 38:02.824
Till the foul crimes
done in my days of nature

38:02.826 --> 38:05.026
are burnt and purged away.

38:11.934 --> 38:14.569
But for that I am forbid

38:14.571 --> 38:16.438
