start from their spheres.

38:26.216 --> 38:29.416
Got your coat.

38:35.057 --> 38:36.390
Charlie.

38:36.392 --> 38:37.725
Dawn.

38:37.727 --> 38:39.059
You know Giselle?

38:39.061 --> 38:41.528
Uh, we haven't met officially. Hi.

38:41.530 --> 38:43.364
I'm staying with her for the weekend.

38:43.366 --> 38:45.699
